{
  "stem": "23815.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They told us to undo all the clothing, because the Germans knew it, that Jewish people got money.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they got jewelry.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they got diamonds, whatever they have-- to tear them apart.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they used to bring us suitcases so-- so we can put it in.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Separate the diamonds.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Separate the gold.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And separate the money.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we used to stack those things-- those jewelries, and diamonds, and money-- hundreds and hundreds of suitcases every day. 'Cause when they burned the people, they used to bring to us the-- the clothing.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was doing this, Pauline, for one year.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Can you imagine how many diamonds, and how many gold, and how many-- how much money I used to pick?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Not only me, I mean, we were quite a few women there that we were doing-- day after day.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I used to play with the diamonds.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't care about them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I didn't want them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It didn't mean nothing to me, because the suffering was enough.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But we used to packed every day hundreds of suitcases.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was not pleasant.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But you had to do it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "If somebody put a gun on your-- on your back, on your head, and-- and-- and tell you you have to do it, you do it.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You want to save yourself.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That's what-- that was-- we were doing there for one year in this-- in the-- Auschwitz, just where-- where the crematoriums was.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They didn't know where they're going.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They didn't.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it was breaking my heart.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And after what we did that, besides that, we tore apart the clothing.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We used to put the men clothing separate, women separate, children separate.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
